Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿旅行一定很愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡有藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶海景的雪白的西式旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的陽臺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把學美的那份也喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不要喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我的那份喝了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別？
