Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我是不會動搖的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  今天是第一次在學校以外的地方和小芽一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「特別」～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是在玩  不是在打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好了  休息時間結束了  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  咦  最輕鬆自在的不是小芽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你們拿來續杯的飲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是蜜柑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要去你們那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我剛想接電話  不小心摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森同學  你在玩甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  Shutter Chance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起基本入會免費宣傳中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生們放暑假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕她們這麼清閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假之所以特別  大概是因為它的構成要素很Special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構成要素？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Special？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好萊塢的超大作  很Special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能疊上五個  很Special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連涼麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是暑假Special菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  暑假=特別  證明結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都幸苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱的天有勞大家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我說  工作根本就沒怎麼進行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧得小芽都在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真沒面子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這個  我們學生才會被那些打工的小瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  在說甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼都沒說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我的那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水槍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  「特別」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  「特別」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒～甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假  是學生獨有的特別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為從事報導工作的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定繼續追尋這份特別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到零食店了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:08.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速列車馬上就要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:12.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請退到黃線後等待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹茶味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇打味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後  我是宇治金時味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  很完美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勺子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯了換乘列車  光是聯絡就等了一個半小時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假期間可以隨意乘坐的慢車  學生18號票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜兩日的聖櫻學生會特別合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有預先看一下天氣預報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按…按照性格來說  這是小芽應該做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  蜜柑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  剛剛還在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕  咕嚕  咕嚕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蜜柑被吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  快去救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼這裡連便利店的影子都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是…鄉下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在2035年不可能有這種事發生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先找住的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕  咕嚕  咕嚕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的難道是蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跌進水田裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  快去救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  真的不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  錢我已經打進網路帳戶裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太打擾別人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是  原本計劃要去的旅館我退掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你  我們毫無準備也能直接入住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會給別人添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正把我們帶到房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯  那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這種樣式的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十點結賬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急出口在二樓的左側
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娛樂室在一樓的東面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室到晚上一點為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來小芽的最可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫下來～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱裡的食物要額外算錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你在做甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天宮同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脫掉…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回聖櫻學園學生會潛水大賽的優勝者是學美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,115  快撥115！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是國內電報！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的  別睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要給我無緣無故就倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把體育新聞關了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是會胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個總該存有目的意識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是把舉行合宿的原因給忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的合宿\N是為了迎接學園祭而使大家意識統一才舉辦的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…大家一起玩這個怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾不能去帶海景的西式旅館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧海藍天和雪白的西式旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有可愛的陽臺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對這些條件做了選擇而預訂了旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本一定會有十分特別的回憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是學生小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  合宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這樣的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我沒上過高中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  卻沒有後悔過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟繼承這家旅館是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  還是儘早來這裡好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個時代這麼做是被認可的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個性急的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒想過有甚麼想做的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一無所長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像學美時常精神百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦很擅長體育
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動神經也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃也在報導部努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽學習很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣再想想我的話  就感覺被落下好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連未來的事都沒有考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是茫然地在高中讀書…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了這個才去上高中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必心急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事  不久之後就會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去整理一下「菊之間」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  是我拉住她聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是學生小姐您的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很久沒和與自己同代的人聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能和朋友一起進行暑假旅行真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也經常去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太吵了給店員惹了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上還一起起勁地聊著心儀男生的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我本來想讓那孩子去讀高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那孩子無論怎樣都想來這裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說甚麼與其去讀高中  還不如來這裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得這樣可以就同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我認為去學校的意義\N不僅僅在於「找到自己想做的事」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不僅僅在於此」  是甚麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  總有一天你也會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能理解這麼深奧的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎樣去做  也得不出結論
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在滿腦子想的全是學園祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得在這家旅館也充滿了很多特別的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要是也這麼想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假  能被理解成學生們的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於學生的特殊時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被叫做答案的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就包含在這個影像中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聖櫻學園的櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事想和您通電話談談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請講吧
